{"tid":1308899,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蔣麗芸：曾考慮倡設獨立委員會調查修例風波","createTime":"2019-07-12T04:14:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T10:38:15.000Z","uid":275588,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"94758650923b8ab05a6a8fea292db61507d8bf91","tid":1308899,"uid":275588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:14:49.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】民建聯立法會議員蔣麗芸出席本台節目《時事全方位》，透露曾考慮提出成立獨立調查委員會，調查逃犯條例修訂風波的來龍去脈，但擔心會令議會再陷入紛爭而作罷。<br />\n<br />\n蔣麗芸：「監警會僅針對調查其他人投訴，其實我覺得某程度比調查委員會更嚴厲，因為它只調查警察。當時我想提出動議調查整件事來龍去脈，還有大家知道背後很多資源，很多支持，錢從何來。後來研究都是放棄(獨立調查不是很好？)只會令議會再度強烈爭議。」<br />\n<br />\n尹兆堅：「我不介意調查整件事，除了警方濫暴外，其他環節如政府缺失、諮詢過程差，有甚麼事做得不好，甚至他們(建制派)所說指控，雖然我覺得子虛烏有，甚麼外國資金，一併調查。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=355134\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D355134&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0Fiy1AgKJyIubMvfhItfpFI%3D&h=be78b06d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D355134&h=e2c749aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=355134</a>"},{"pid":"0bc5083bac5196c0c8be563b1a38700042695866","tid":1308899,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:16:05.000Z","msg":"ann姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20511845979b3ec860f4ea14e173f522cbbfb4db","tid":1308899,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:17:26.000Z","msg":"呢個蠢人有份送政府一程"},{"pid":"2acda651c6d4fc694e7eb9d3ebb7e334d0e37633","tid":1308899,"uid":267730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:18:22.000Z","msg":"佢仲以為自己果邊未死得"},{"pid":"3029bfdf64edf5720dbb7695377fa6cad826cd3a","tid":1308899,"uid":4619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:18:23.000Z","msg":"支持Ann姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d